"I
thank
you;
but
I
assure
you
you
are
quite
mistaken.
Mr.
Elton
and
I
are
very
good
friends,
and
nothing
more;"
and
she
walked
on,
amusing
herself
in
the
consideration
of
the
blunders
which
often
arise
from
a
partial
